"Missing `GITLAB_TOKEN` or `GITLAB_PROJECT_PATH` causes the endpoint to "
"return `503 GITLAB_NOT_CONFIGURED`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ciou-gitlab-integration.md:94
